title: Quick Take: Wisconsin Primary Results
description: Campaign reporter Scott Detrow and political editor Domenico Montanaro discuss results from the Democratic and Republican primaries in Wisconsin. Find them on Twitter @scottdetrow and @DomenicoNPR, or write the show at nprpolitics@npr.org. More coverage at nprpolitics.org.
